{"tid":1028703,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"廿四味 24Herbs 《無撚用》\"M.L.Y\" [歌詞道出香港人心聲]","createTime":"2019-02-19T16:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T17:16:41.000Z","uid":106937,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e561001250b8980226fca9190ecbc5da3b7155de","tid":1028703,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vGzhrOK6HYY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvGzhrOK6HYY&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=cdcfe26c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vGzhrOK6HYY</a> <br />\n<br />\n《無撚用》<br />\n<br />\n你間屋真係堅堅係衰到冇人租<br />\n就好似你個ig鋪極相都冇人follow<br />\n講到點四正點好根本睇唔到<br />\n我只睇到shit hole同隻打唔開嘅window<br />\n一步就到 喂你咪阻住條路<br />\n一劏12嘅玩法去死啦你要趁早<br />\n為咗錢乜都做有磚頭先叫王道<br />\n理得你瞓喺shit hole佢照戴金撈<br />\n有冇人可以話俾我知道<br />\n仲住得人嘅香港究竟去咗邊度 得個做<br />\n索性把心一橫呃政府綜援仲着數<br />\n我都想有咁厚面皮唯有繼續R撈<br />\n<br />\n*做幾多搵幾多儲幾多都冇撚用<br />\n做幾多搵幾多儲幾多都冇撚用<br />\n做幾多搵幾多儲幾多都冇撚用<br />\n做幾多搵幾多儲幾多都冇撚用<br />\n(起勢猛做 起勢猛做 起勢猛做 冇撚用 )<br />\n(不停咁儲 不停咁儲 不停咁儲 冇撚用 )<br />\n(起勢猛做 起勢猛做 起勢猛做 冇撚用 )<br />\n(不停咁儲 不停咁儲 儲幾多都冇撚用)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成舊水去食個把撚茶記<br />\n最乏味係 要受嗰班仆街氣 當正我臭四<br />\n貼錢買難受 佢照舊 理𨳊你<br />\nd物價指數貴撚到Fucking離曬地<br />\n仲猛咁叫你借貸買呀買呀根本係想你死<br />\nd福利派呀派呀派曬俾 落嚟嗰百幾<br />\n我真係恭喜你呀香港地<br />\n李嘉欣呢一句說話先至夠貼地<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\nSave dough, 你話好唔好? 香港生活指數做到80都儲唔到<br />\n漫長路, when the money flows?<br />\n廿四小時日做夜做根本就唔對路<br />\n我 work work work work work 得個桔<br />\n你掠掠掠掠掠似拮屎忽<br />\nThey say 1 foot 60 K, that's what you want me to pay?<br />\nI fucking got more chance to levitate then own a bit of real estate.<br />\n<br />\nI ain't goin no where, goin away, this is my hood I'll be here all the way.<br />\nGoin no where, goin away, Eight Five Two I'ma rep it all day.<br />\nWe just wanna breath, we ain't complaining<br />\nWe just wanna breath, shit's so frustrating<br />\nWe just wanna breath, we ain't complaining<br />\nWe just wanna breath, this is what I'm saying<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\nWorking for the man, got me some cash<br />\n15 years&hellip;eating nothing but trash<br />\n15 years&hellip;gone like that<br />\n1.5mil in my bank stash<br />\n250 feet&hellip;all I can get<br />\nMortgage payments making me sweat<br />\n2 hours ride home, just to get back<br />\n6 months later, I fucking got sacked"},{"pid":"4e226145001256edba0af32427e7d7f4146cdf17","tid":1028703,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T16:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afac466fb3b247cb6c23da1cb87d6574ea63ad7f","tid":1028703,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T16:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fd6b6f82753d3c528a621db8f25593304cf872","tid":1028703,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"死link"},{"pid":"3643fa0396f9602ae99bfd2d6fa6a3f709374a32","tid":1028703,"uid":17541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:56:10.000Z","msg":"JBS嗰段正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj